{"tid":1462341,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聯合國：警違規發射催淚彈證據確鑿　籲港府調查 (17:54)","createTime":"2019-08-13T10:24:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T10:29:27.000Z","uid":214502,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"64b7253a0883a495d8cd088f5bed5df6c79e7f5a","tid":1462341,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:24:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190813/s00001/1565689257018/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%9C%8B-%E8%AD%A6%E9%81%95%E8%A6%8F%E7%99%BC%E5%B0%84%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88%E8%AD%89%E6%93%9A%E7%A2%BA%E9%91%BF-%E7%B1%B2%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190813%2Fs00001%2F1565689257018%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E5%259C%258B-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2581%2595%25E8%25A6%258F%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B0%2584%25E5%2582%25AC%25E6%25B7%259A%25E5%25BD%2588%25E8%25AD%2589%25E6%2593%259A%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E9%2591%25BF-%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5&d=HBLsGxwPt4tNlCAdiZVEvtagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=a4a7ecbe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190813%2Fs00001%2F1565689257018%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E5%259C%258B-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2581%2595%25E8%25A6%258F%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B0%2584%25E5%2582%25AC%25E6%25B7%259A%25E5%25BD%2588%25E8%25AD%2589%25E6%2593%259A%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E9%2591%25BF-%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5&h=c53c3750\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190813/s00001/1565689257018/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%9C%8B-%E8%AD%A6%E9%81%95%E8%A6%8F%E7%99%BC%E5%B0%84%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88%E8%AD%89%E6%93%9A%E7%A2%BA%E9%91%BF-%E7%B1%B2%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5</a><br />\n香港修訂《逃犯條例》引發多場警民衝突，其中警方發射催淚彈手法引起爭議。聯合國人權事務高級專員巴切萊特（Michelle Bachelet）透過發言人發表聲明，表示現時已有證據證明香港警方已違反指引，向示威者發射催淚彈，呼籲港府調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n聲明表示，觀察到警方針對人群密集式發射、直接針對單獨示威者發射，以及在密閉空間或以近距離形式發射催淚彈，很可能會造成示威者重傷甚至死亡。發言人又表示，港澳辦稱香港反修例示威出現「恐怖主義苗頭」的說法，無助緩和、甚至有可能使局勢惡化。<br />\n<br />\n警方前晚（11日）在港鐵葵芳站內施放催淚彈，涉事催淚彈供應商的指引列明只可於室外使用。警察公共關係科高級警司江永祥昨日（12日）在記者會上解釋，考慮到葵芳站是半開放式，非設於地底，警員經評估後施放一枚催淚彈，當時亦發射兩發橡膠子彈。至於為何警員不入站拘捕，他稱考慮很多因素，包括現場煙霧瀰漫及有示威者攻擊警員等。<br />\n（路透社）"},{"pid":"ad2c7f46b9a9733f0d6a3dfc3c8886426fa479fd","tid":1462341,"uid":8776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:29:27.000Z","msg":"呼籲港府調查<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}